{
  "texts": [
    "We prompted the model to translate the manuscript sentence by sentence.",
    "We ran a first pass in which we sent requests for the entire manuscript.",
    "Of the 755 sentences in OT-EN dataset, 208 sentences, or 27%, were not translated.",
    "We know from previous experiments that sometimes these models can behave in an unexpected way and simply not translate.",
    "Thus, we ran a second pass on these 208 sentences using the same translation prompt."
  ]
}